name:                ?abort
stack:               ( flag -- )
return stack:        ( -- )
string stack:        ( -- )
contexts:            stateless
category:            flow control, error handling

decription:          a non-zero value for flag aborts, passing u as abort value to
                     error handling.  if flag is zero, both flag und u are removed
                     and execution continues.

notes:               not entirely unlike "assert" known from some other languages.
